Introduction

Lady was a four-member girl group under Logi Entertainment in which all the members were transgender. They debuted on April 7, 2005, with the mini album, "Attention".

In February 2007, the group disbanded because of the discrimination that Lady was receiving from the Korean public, and for not generating profit for the company.
